'''Franco Sacchi numukinnyi''' wa firime wumutaliyani akaba n'umwanditsi . <ref>https://www.ted.com/speakers/franco_sacchi</ref> Azwi cyane nk'umuyobozi wa firime zizwi cyane ''Iyi Ni Nollywood'', ''Inkone z'Abanyamerika'' no ''Gutegereza Harimagedoni'' . <ref>https://www2.bfi.org.uk/films-tv-people/4ce2bd1204ccb</ref> <ref>https://mubi.com/cast/franco-sacchi</ref>

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavukiye muri [[Zambiya]] akurira mu Butaliyani. <ref>https://vimeo.com/francosacchi</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Mu 2003, yakoze documentaire ye ya mbere ''y'Abanyamerika Inkone'' . Filime yerekanwe kandi itoranywa kumugaragaro muri International Documentary Film Festival Amsterdam (IDFA). Muri 2005, yakoze icyerekezo ''IThis Is Nollywood'',documentaire ivuga ibijyanye ninganda za firime . <ref>https://ted2srt.org/talks/franco_sacchi_a_tour_of_nollywood_nigeria_s_booming_film_industry</ref> Filime yaje gutsindira igihembo cyabaterankunga mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya firime rya Abuja. Iyo filime igenda neza, Franco yafatanije kuyobora no gufata amashusho ''Waiting for Armageddon'',, yasohotse mu 2010. <ref name="Franco">http://www.francosacchi.com/about-us/</ref>

Usibye kuyobora firime, yabaye umwarimu mukuru muri Avid Technology kuva 1996 kugeza 2002. <ref name="Franco" />

